### for developer usage, syntax I always forgot.

drop db in psql:
drop database "nt_project_test";

set up test db:
rake db:test:prepare

run test:
ruby test/relation_test.rb      

heroku:
heroku create
heroku addons:create heroku-postgresql:hobby-dev
git push heroku main
heroku open
heroku logs
git add .
git push heroku main